### Get all customers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/customer
Accept: application/json

### Get a single customer by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/customer/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Accept: application/json

### Create a new customer
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/customer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
  "name": "John Doe"
}

### Update an existing customer
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/customer/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe"
}
